newsitem.title: SINGAPORE: Singapore bunker final report and prices- Nov 13.
newsitem.headline: Singapore bunker final report and prices- Nov 13.

text.p: DELIVERED U.S.$/TONNE) 380 CST 180 CST MDO GAS OIL

COMMENTS - Bunker prices ended around Tuesday's range, in line with stable cargo prices but enquiries were very thin, traders said on Wednesday. They said shipowners were mostly sidelined in anticipation of prices easing and were in no hurry to cover their requirements. "I guess they could afford to wait," said a major. MDO and gasoil were firmer, tracking higher gas oil prices.
